WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:12.760
Llanmais Church is dedicated to St Cadwc. On one of the walls can be found the remains

00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:22.800
of a painting of St George slaying the dragon. This is very interesting because in Llancarbon

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:32.800
Church, a site of the monastery of St Cadwc, there has recently been found a wall painting

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.480
also of St George slaying the dragon.

